diff a/docs/API.md b/docs/API.md	(rejected hunks)
@@ -23,7 +23,8 @@ Base URL: `/api`
 
 ## Data
 
-- `GET /api/sb/rows?table=<name>&limit=100&offset=0&order=<col>&desc=<true|false>`
+- `GET /api/sb/rows?table=<name>&limit=100&offset=0&order=<col>&desc=<true|false>&filter=<col>.<op>.<val>`
+  - `filter` can be repeated; each becomes a PostgREST param, e.g. `filter=name.ilike.%foo%` → `name=ilike.%foo%`.
   - Response: `{ rows: any[], total: number|null, limit, offset }`
   - Uses `Prefer: count=exact` to read total from `Content-Range`.
 - `GET /api/sb/row?table=<name>&id=<val>&pk=id` → `{ row: any|null }`
